        <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
        <description>While the standard number verification in SDL Trados Studio may often be sufficient there are some occasions when a bit more control would be preferable, for example when translating documents that contain lots of numbers, especially when they are non-standard. This Number Verifier plug-in allows you to fine-tune settings to provide you with the desired balance between amount of false positives and potentially missed errors.</description>
